                                                These buckets start at a feerate of 1 sat/byte and <a target="_blank" href="/txt/200buckets.txt">increase 5% each bucket</a>.
                                                <a target="_blank" href="https://bitcointechtalk.com/an-introduction-to-bitcoin-core-fee-estimation-27920880ad0">This article</a> gives some insight on Core's fee estimation using buckets and targets for v0.14, however there were <a target="_blank" href="https://gist.github.com/morcos/d3637f015bc4e607e1fd10d8351e9f41#proposed-changes-for-015">some improvements</a> in v0.15.
